import '../styles/Projects.sass' function Projects(){ return

PROJECTS

Stravita, is a small clone from strava It's a social media web aplication (mobile first) designed for register and share sport activities.

User can track their activities with the main focus on the elevation gain, and distance.

The application shows some data in real time like altitude, distance, time, weather and map including the track registered.

Checkout Github repositorie for more information.
} export default Projects
